OL,3,CInside the #988m Midland Metropolitan
OL,4,CHospital set to open in October
OL,6,FThe Midland Metropolitan University
OL,7,FHospital, which is set to open on
OL,8,FOctober 6, will provide healthcare for
OL,9,Fpeople in the Black Country and
OL,10,FBirmingham.
OL,12,FThe hospital, located in Smethwick,
OL,13,Fwill replace Sandwell General Hospital
OL,14,Fand City Hospital A&E departments and
OL,15,Fwill be run by four and a half
OL,16,Fthousand NHS staff.
