OL,4,CHospital set to open in October
OL,6,FThe hospital was supposed to open in
OL,7,F2018, but the collapse of
OL,8,FWolverhampton based construction
OL,9,Fcompany Carillion and then coronavirus
OL,10,F- brought delay after delay.
OL,12,FNursing staff are convinced they'll be
OL,13,Fable to spend more time at a patients
OL,14,Fside.
