OL,4,CHospital set to open in October
OL,6,FOne nurse said: "We have isolation
OL,7,Frooms which means that I can talk to
OL,8,Fthe patient on the intercom, see what
OL,9,Fthey require, get what they need, and
OL,10,Fthen put protective gear on and then
OL,11,Fgo into the patient, so we are not
OL,12,Fwasting time put our protective gear
OL,13,Fon and off a number of times."
OL,15,FThe cost wound up being - more than
OL,16,Fdouble the original estimate -
OL,17,Freaching over 988m pounds while the
OL,18,Fnew hospitals capacity - is actually
OL,19,Fsmaller than the two its replacing.
