OL,6,FLewis Warner asked the Chief Executive
OL,7,Fof the trust if this was a mistake:
OL,9,FChief Executive of the trust, Richard
OL,10,FBeeken said: "The business case was
OL,11,Fwritten ten years ago and demand has
OL,12,Fchanged since then. We are the only
OL,13,Ftrusted within Birmingham and the
OL,14,Fblack country who's hospital admission
OL,15,Fis going down, not up."
OL,17,FThe ambulance service is hoping it can
OL,18,Fbegin to avoid long handover delays.
